name: COVID19ICD10PCSValueSetForRenalDialysis
title: COVID19 ICD10PCS Value Set for Renal Dialysis
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to renal dialysis procedures and is listed as a renal disorder on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes renal dialysis procedures such as hemodialysis, peritoneal dialysis and dialysis access procedures. It also includes terms related to the intial placement of renal dialysis catheter.),(Exclusion Criteria: )
